		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.47]</nobr><br><br><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Ry'Gor armor is the way to go.&nbsp;&nbsp;Use jewelry to get your CHA and DEX up.  DEX helps prevent missed notes.  CHA helps with charm, lull, and mezz songs.  Get Crested Spaulders (about 150pp) for your shoulders. Good AC and they help with STA. You want STA=100 or slightly better so you don't fatique in combat.  Most of the time JJV works but you may not always have the chance to play it. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222</a><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760</a></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
